{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586860/extras/Bonesaw_Gameplay_loop_crop.gif?t=1736521606\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bonesaw: Gambling Severed Fingers!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal is to eliminate both of your opponents' hands to save yourself from eternal damnation. This is the Devil's game, and he's out to claim your soul... and your fingers! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586860/extras/Steam_Gif_Bonesaw_SawSpinning5.GIF?t=1736521606\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Saw: Unnerving and Cruel</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adding fear and chaos to the mix, the saw is part of a bloodthirsty contraption that punishes players by cutting off their fingers! Combining skill with a little luck, the blade can be controlled to your advantage. Will you be brave enough to ring the bell to unleash it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586860/extras/Bonesaw_Loop_chip-Steam.gif?t=1736521606\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Items: Diverse and Versatile</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategize carefully, steal from your opponent or combine the effects of various items to take the upper hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586860/extras/Bonesaw_Power.png?t=1736521606\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Skeleton: Neutral yet Highly Rewarding</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep an eye on ALL players around the table\u2026who knows what rewards are granted to those who eliminate the skeleton first? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586860/extras/M_Picture_Steam_01_small.png?t=1736521606\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiple Game Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play through a gripping single player experience with different game modes or challenge a friend in local multiplayer or online with Steam Remote Play. Who wouldn't want to chop their friend's fingers off\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How To Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Goal:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The first player to accumulate 3 points (win 3 rounds) wins the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To win a round, players must be the first to eliminate both of their opponent\u2019s hands. A hand is removed from play when its total finger count is reached or when it\u2019s severed by the saw.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Player Turn:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play chips and power cards to gain special abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attack an opponent\u2019s hand and add the number of fingers from your attacking hand to theirs. If the attack total exceeds the number of fingers on the targeted hand, the count resets and the remaining amount is added.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attack the bell to activate the saw. Additional attacks on the bell will move the blade clockwise around the active hands to have it target another hand.\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The skeleton is a passive side player. Be the first to eliminate him to earn a power card, granting a unique and game-changing ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When active, the saw has a chance to sever a hand at the end of each turn. The gauge surrounding the bell displays the chances of the saw cutting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every finger lost changes drastically the dynamic and strategies of the following rounds!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Deliverance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/d8a367298c61ff87b73ba68b375b0b96652a5b68.jpg"},{"name":"Mutilated","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/c94a479a95743ac339e37d9f6314aa258aab2dce.jpg"},{"name":"Dealer\u2019s Downfall","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/7fd49fc7a84aeb443f1a621be418dd56642f32b6.jpg"},{"name":"He\u2019s Already Dead Anyways\u2026","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/4eea13381da10883e4adc68c2fc4f12885c8bb3a.jpg"},{"name":"Unlucky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/a5db73c257891a6af3155fb7c919905b4847ac63.jpg"},{"name":"Merry-Go-Round Of Death","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/6a9ef49908e063f78e35513de0d38a9b9a3fbaea.jpg"},{"name":"What A Mess","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/2647ed4e4a61d10564a8431cf18c742a4be54bcf.jpg"},{"name":"A Powerful Deck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/eaa416432da54a88fbacd2f9f17ee936b5ed494c.jpg"},{"name":"All In","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/42ece7813af21111089a21ddd40dd70817571b6f.jpg"},{"name":"Honor Among Thieves","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1586860/f93b6a142277e793228fe494e0ac85935f570358.jpg"}],"total":25},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586860/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736521606","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586860